title: Sushi Visa/Mastercard
body:
Create a cryptocurrency to fiat funded debit card. SUSHI CARD.
Starting with Sushi and then adding main cryto pairs.
It will help to expand the DeFi ecosystem and the utility of Sushi.
A decentralized model similar to Monolith or Swipe could be the blueprint.
